This is the Perl distribution App-perlzonji.

## Installation

App-perlzonji installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is
set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan App::perlzonji

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

## Documentation

App-perlzonji documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc App::perlzonji

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

